OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,FReform Warwickshire County Council
OL,8,Fleader George Finch has survived a
OL,9,Fvote to oust him.
OL,11,FIn a nail-biting vote at Shire Hall on
OL,12,FTuesday, March 17, the Bedworth
OL,13,FCentral representative fought off a
OL,14,Fbid to remove him as leader. But it
OL,15,Fwas a tight vote after a more than two
OL,16,Fhour long debate at Shire Hall this
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,FGreen Party leader Cllr Jonathan
OL,8,FChilvers tabled the motion at the full
OL,9,Fcouncil meeting which asked for a vote
OL,10,Fof no confidence to be shown in Cllr
OL,11,FFinch, effectively removing him as
OL,12,Fleader.
OL,14,FThere were two councillors who made
OL,15,Fapologies for the meeting, so that
OL,16,Fleft 55 councillors to decide if they
OL,17,Fwere going to support the motion.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,FWhen it came to the vote, there were
OL,8,F26 in favour of the motion, 27 against
OL,9,Fand two abstentions. This meant that
OL,10,FCllr Finch won the vote to remain
OL,11,Fleader by one single vote.
OL,13,FIt was the Conservatives who proved to
OL,14,Fbe king-makers with Tory group leader,
OL,15,FCllr Adrian Warwick, explaining prior
OL,16,Fto the vote: "It has been a very, very
OL,17,Fdifficult time for my group to sit and
OL,18,Fdiscuss where we go.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,F"Have mistakes been made? Yes, they
OL,8,Fhave. I think that he (Cllr Finch) has
OL,9,Falluded himself that his language
OL,10,Fcould be better at times.
OL,12,F"I think he needs to reflect on
OL,13,Fattacks that have been made across the
OL,14,Fline at my group."
OL,16,FBut he added that process matters and,
OL,17,Ftalking to Cllr Finch, he said: "If
OL,18,Fyou get through today's vote, I hope
OL,19,Fyou take on board the comments of
OL,20,Ftoday, learn because we have to count.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,F"We need some stability in this
OL,8,Fchamber. There has to be."
OL,10,FCllr Finch himself gave a speech in
OL,11,Fwhich he explained that it was the
OL,12,Fvoters who should decide who should be
OL,13,Fleader, not a "coalition of chaos".
OL,15,FThe 19-year-old defended himself and
OL,16,Fsaid: ""This is not about
OL,17,Faccountability, good standards and
OL,18,Fgovernance.
OL,26,@xD@HOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,F"This is not just aimed at me but it
OL,8,Fis aimed at the entire Reform group in
OL,9,FWarwickshire. It is aimed at
OL,10,Foverturning the will of the people in
OL,11,FWarwickshire.
OL,13,F"Since I took over in July, this
OL,14,Fcouncil has been moving in the right
OL,15,Fdirection and a determination to
OL,16,Fdeliver for the people of Warwickshire.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,F"We are here to serve the people who
OL,8,Fsent us here, not the people in this
OL,9,Fchamber, not the political bubble The
OL,10,Fpeople in the towns and villages who
OL,11,Fexpect us to get on with this job."
OL,13,FCllr Chilvers, who had tabled the
OL,14,Fmotion, claimed that Cllr Finch's
OL,15,Faction had undermined the work of the
OL,16,Fcouncil and Warwickshire as a whole.
OL,18,FHe said that he has "fallen short"
OL,19,Fafter asking to be judged on his
OL,20,Frecord of his actions of leader.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1773831918
OL,3,CReform UK council leader George Finch
OL,4,Csurvives nail biting vote of no
OL,5,Cconfidence
OL,7,F"The charge sheet against councillor
OL,8,FFinch is longer than his 34 weeks in
OL,9,Fpower," he said. "Enough damage to
OL,10,FWarwickshire County Council," he added.
OL,12,FHe said that he was "sad" to table the
OL,13,Fmotion, but added that Cllr Finch has
OL,14,F"repeatedly shown he is not the right
OL,15,Fperson" to lead Warwickshire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
